Package model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Postcondition
    Describes the changes made to a state.
    Precondition
    Describes the requirements.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Action
    An action that can be executed.
    Goal
    The goal is described by a set of requirements.
    Plan
    A plan consists of a set of actions and a cost.
    Planner
    The planner manages planning algorithms.
    Scenario
    A scenario consists of a start state, a goal and a set of actions.
    State
    A state is a collection of custom integer variables.
